          <a href="https://millercenter.org/the-presidency/presidential-speeches/june-7-2001-remarks-signing-economic-growth-and-tax-relief">Miller Center: June 7, 2001: Remarks on Signing the Economic Growth and Tax Relief Reconciliation Act</a>
